query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('asp.net-web-api2',
'com',
'compiler-construction',
'global-variables',
'html-email',
'http-post',
'react-navigation',
'signalr',
'toggle',
'uiimageview',
'windows-phone-7');
